videos.description: Jamal Johnson blocks the layup attempt of Cincinnati's Jarron Cumberland at the basket.
videos.headline: Memphis' Johnson rejects Cumberland at the rim

videos.description: Justin Jenifer cuts through the defense and scores a high-arcing jumper for the Bearcats.
videos.headline: Cincinnati's Jenifer crosses over defender and scores

videos.description: Jeremiah Martin displays beautiful body control for a left-handed layup and is foul for an old-fashioned 3-point play.
videos.headline: Memphis' Martin scores fast- break layup

videos.description: Jacob Cumberland hits a 3-pointer to cap an 8-0 run for the Bearcats.
videos.headline: Cumberland buries transition 3-pointer

videos.description: Jarron Cumberland drives and makes a layup to extend Cincinnati's lead.
videos.headline: Cumberland gets to the rim and scores layup

videos.description: Kareen Brewton uses an up-and-under move, makes the basket and is fouled for a three-point play.
videos.headline: Memphis' Brewton shows slick moves down low

videos.description: Kareem Brewton shakes Jacob Evans, drives to the cup and muscles in for a layup off the glass.
videos.headline: Brewton shows wicked handles on layup

videos.description: Bearcats extend their home winning streak to 34 games with a 82-48 victory over Memphis behind Gary Clark's 13 points and 10 rebounds.  .
videos.headline: Cincinnati cruises to an easy home victory over Memphis
